headline: FBN Expands AI-Powered Platform for Ag Commerce, Financing, and Farm Intelligence
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., July 28, 2025--Farmers Business Network (FBN®), the collaborative peer-to-peer farmer network generating farm-level intelligence and a leading marketplace for North America's agricultural sector, announced new investments and platform expansions alongside $50 million in funding to fuel new product lines and AI deployment.
